history.content: Many upper divs will be able to open up the remaining seats that are already posted as part of the full enrollment limit/class capacity in the schedule of classes but are currently blocked pending hiring of full gsi/ugsi staffing.   It is highly unlikely that any of the classes will be expanded to larger than the existing publicly displayed full class size.

Is it typical for some of the CS upper divs offered to be expanded in size? If so, which have been the most likely to expand in the past? Which look most likely (if at all) to expand this upcoming semester?
history.subject: CS Course Expansions
